{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_05_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 寄ってらっしゃい見てらっしゃい！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "さあさあ、寄ってらっしゃい見てらっしゃい！\n美味しい美味しい海の家だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ come on‚ come and see!\nIt's a delicious‚ delicious beach restaurant!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前に芽衣は何をやってるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is Mei doing before the live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、凄い混みようだな\n……呼び込み方はちょっと変だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it's really crowded.\n…The way she's calling people is a bit strange‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 11.533333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 19.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "はいはーい！　オススメのメニュー？\nうーん、そうだなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! Recommended menu?\nHmm‚ let's see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 26.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣のオススメは焼きそばだよ！\nさっき食べたらすっごく美味しかった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei's recommendation is yakisoba!\nI had it earlier and it was really delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、焼きそばにしてくれる？\nはーい、焼きそば二つ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you want yakisoba?\nYes‚ two orders of yakisoba‚ please~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたの？\nかき氷を食べたいの？　オッケー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What's the matter?\nYou want to eat shaved ice? Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 47.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どーぞ。急いで食べると頭がキーンって\nしちゃうから、ゆっくり食べてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here you go. If you eat it too quickly‚ you'll get brain freeze‚\nso take your time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　なになに？　この衣装が可愛い？\n嬉しいな、ありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What is it? You think this costume is cute?\nI'm so happy‚ thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 64.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "この後ね、これを着てみんなの前で歌うんだよ\nえ、見に来てくれるの？　ありがとー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After this‚ I'll wear this and sing in front of everyone.\nEh‚ you're coming to watch? Thank you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 73.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（邪魔をするようで悪いけど……）\n（さすがにそろそろ止めないとな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I feel bad for interfering…）\n（I should probably stop her soon.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣。一体何をしてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ what exactly are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 81
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "わっ。{user}さん\nバレちゃったかー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nSo you found out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1051424149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、やっぱり我慢出来なくなっちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I just couldn't resist it after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 92.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、おじいちゃん！　こっちは大丈夫だよ\n芽衣がばっちりやってるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Grandpa! Don't worry about me‚\nMei is doing great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 98.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！\n料理は気長にゆっくり待っててねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone!\nBe patient and wait for the food‚ okay~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "そのかわりとっても美味しいから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in return‚ it's really delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.3333333999944,
          "startTime": 106.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしてこんなことをしてるのかと思ったけど……）\n（なるほど、あのおじいさんをずっと心配してたんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was wondering why she was doing this…）\n（I see‚ she was just really worried about that grandpa.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣。ライブ前なんだし、無理だけはするなよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ it's right before the live performance‚ so don't push yourself too hard‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 119.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった、ほどほどにしとくね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand. I'll take it easy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 123.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんは\n芽衣のこと、怒らないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san‚\nAren't you angry with Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前だろ？　俺は芽衣のマネージャーなんだから\nお見通しだよ。そういうことなら、仕方ないと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not. I'm your manager‚ after all.\nI understand you. If that's the case‚ I can't do anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 136.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか、ありがとう\nよーし、張り切ってどんどん呼び込んじゃうから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see‚ thank you.\nAlright‚ I'll be enthusiastic and keep calling people!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
